    <section class="ta-hero">
        <h1>Tamil Alphabet Charts</h1>
        <p>Walk into any bookstore and you'll find alphabet charts filled with giraffes, penguins, and macaws. But what about the creatures that are around us? This chart brings together the plants and animals of Tamil Nadu, from dugongs to Indrella snails, fungi, odonates, wasps, wildflowers — all through the Tamil alphabet. Produced to introduce the biodiversity of Tamil Nadu through the Tamil alphabets for kids, teachers, and nature educators.</p>
    </section>

